Querela Pacis (1518) f0. 0⁴. Louvain. Lond. xxix. 15: LB. i. 535. 13 March 1518.

[The Encomium artis medicae, to which this is the preface, was one of Erasmus' early compositions ; cf. 1. p. 18. 19-21 and Ep. 95. 11 n. It was one of the addi- tions to Martens’ edition of the Querela Pacis (β : see p. 14) 3 and was printed also in Froben's ‘wedding' volume (cf. Ep. 604. 10 n.) and in γ and δ. The date of this preface is unquestionable. For Afinius see Ep. 542 introd.]
